      "content": "i dont even know what to do anymore. everything is just... debt. every time i think i’m getting ahead, another bill comes or the interest spikes and i’m right back at zero. i feel like i’m just running in circles in a room that’s getting smaller and smaller. there’s literally no way out of this.",
